title: Chicago Hope S02E17 - Life Lines.avi
description:
Dr. Shutt proceeds with Eric Dipretto's psychosurgery while Austin campaigns for the position of chief of surgery and Bix continues to lose control. Dr. Kronk is determined to perform a controversial intestinal transplant on Danny's former boss and good friend, a restauranteur who just wants to enjoy a good meal again. 

More to follow, please give back as much as you take.
